<h4>New Training Item</h4>
<h5>Key Features</h5>
<ul>
		<li>Select a Route</li>
		<li>Training Details</li>
		<li>Training Comment</li>
</ul>

<h5>Select a Route</h5>
<p>If your training was completed on a personal route, select 'Yes'. You
will then be able to select the appropriate route using the route drop down. If
your training was completed on a route known to runnDAILY, but isn't in your
list of routes, you should first navigate to the appropriate route and select
'Record Time'.</p>
<h5>Training Details</h5>
<p>In order to get the most out of your training log, you should fill out
the detail section completely. First, enter a date for your training item. You
may also specify your training type. If you previously selected a route for your
training item, the distance will already be present. Lastly, by providing a time
for your training item, your average pace can be calculated.</p>
<h5>Training Comment</h5>
<p>An optional comment may be entered to describe your training experience.
This comment will be displayed along with the training details wherever training
items are listed.</p>